'''告別賽'''或'''紀念賽'''（{{lang-en|testimonial match}}）是在[[體育|體育]]項目上如英式[[足球|足球]]，球會為長期效力或傑出表現的球員舉行的一場比賽以表彰其對球會的貢獻<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/leeds/content/articles/2005/03/17/sport_united_lucas_radebe_testimonial_feature.shtml|title=BBC - Leeds - Sport - Lucas Radebe: The original Kaiser Chief|work=bbc.co.uk|accessdate=2015-04-29|archive-date=2012-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121111185405/http://www.bbc.co.uk/leeds/content/articles/2005/03/17/sport_united_lucas_radebe_testimonial_feature.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

球會會為那些效力了至少十年而即將離隊或退休的球員舉行，不過有時有些球會效力不足十年，但可能退休或已為球隊作出很大貢獻<ref name=ars>{{cite web|url=http://thearsenalhistory.com/?p=9491|title=Arsenal and testimonial games|work=The Arsenal History|accessdate=1 May 2015|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108131634/http://www.thearsenalhistory.com/?p=9491|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這類賽事一般為非競賽性質，有時還有不少娛樂性十足的場面<ref>{{cite web|url=http://soccer.sina.com.hk/news/1/20150330/4356140/|title=名字替死球線淚灑告別賽|work=香港新浪|accessdate=2015-05-01|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305035740/http://soccer.sina.com.hk/news/1/20150330/4356140/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2626915/Howard-Webb-tackles-Lewis-Holtby-starts-playing-Ledley-King-testimonial-Tottenham-man-returns-upend-referee.html|title=Howard Webb tackles Lewis Holtby and starts playing in Ledley King testimonial... before Tottenham man returns to take out referee - Daily Mail Online|work=Mail Online|accessdate=2015-05-01|archive-date=2017-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170413064412/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2626915/Howard-Webb-tackles-Lewis-Holtby-starts-playing-Ledley-King-testimonial-Tottenham-man-returns-upend-referee.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。通常球員會邀請一些該會名宿或其共事良久的隊友一起出席比賽，這些球員可以是已離隊、甚至只是國家隊的隊友。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/FOOTBALL%3A+No+wonder+it%27s+such+a+shambles.-a074471343|title=FOOTBALL: No wonder it's such a shambles.|work=thefreelibrary.com|accessdate=2015-05-01|archive-date=2019-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211060831/https://www.thefreelibrary.com/FOOTBALL%3A%20No%20wonder%20it%27s%20such%20a%20shambles.-a074471343|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==歷史==
告別賽在1950年代出現，並且在1970至80年代在英國足球普及<ref name=ars/>。告別賽的本意是一些頂級的球會為了對競技水平已不處巔峰、逐漸在球隊暫不住腳的球星作出經濟補償。球會對於這類比賽一般會隆重其事，讓球員賺得一筆可觀的獎金以榮休或另謀高就<ref name=ars/>。告別賽一般都是為份量較大的球星舉辦的另一個原因是這類賽事需要大量球迷撐場，若果該球會規模較小或者該球員的聲望不高，可能會出現入場人數不足的情況而造成尷尬<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2011/jun/22/least-successful-testimonial-match-ever|title=Which is the least successful testimonial match ever?|author=John Ashdown|work=the Guardian|accessdate=2015-05-01|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112024548/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2011/jun/22/least-successful-testimonial-match-ever|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===近年===
告別賽在現今球壇已經較少出現，因為最初用作表揚及經濟補助的用途已經不再合時宜。現時足球員的薪金大漲，效力頂級球會的球員更不愁經濟問題。而且，現時轉會市場更開放，球員很少會留效一支球隊長達十年，加上現時球員轉會普遍，和以前的球員為免受到公眾討伐而避免轉會的情況大相逕庭<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/manchester_united/article3221987.ece|title=Login|work=timesonline.co.uk|accessdate=2015-05-01|archive-date=2008-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201060507/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/manchester_united/article3221987.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/low/sports_talk/1349019.stm|title=BBC SPORT - SPORTS TALK - Should testimonials be scrapped?|work=bbc.co.uk|accessdate=2015-05-01|archive-date=2009-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090607030313/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/low/sports_talk/1349019.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/low/sports_talk/1773136.stm|title=BBC SPORT - SPORTS TALK  - Payback time for footballers?|work=bbc.co.uk|accessdate=2015-05-01|archive-date=2009-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090328165905/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/low/sports_talk/1773136.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.buzzle.com/editorials/8-25-2003-44576.asp |title=Time to Do Away With Testimonials for Rich Footballers<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2015-05-01 |archive-date=2009-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090415182401/http://www.buzzle.com/editorials/8-25-2003-44576.asp |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。不過，現時的告別賽中，那些長期效力一支球會的球星的告別賽依然很受球迷歡迎，入座率很高。

頂級足球界的告別賽仍然會表揚球員，但已漸趨慈善的方向發展，球員會將部份或全部在比賽中籌得的款項全數作為慈善活動。例如{{fc|新特蘭}}和{{nft|愛爾蘭}}國家隊的忠臣[[昆尼|昆尼]]，在2002年於[[光明球場|光明球場]]舉行的友誼賽所得的近一百萬英鎊全數撥捐慈善基金，以支持[[泰恩-威爾郡|泰恩-威爾郡]]、[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]和[[印度|印度]]的兒童醫院<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-114528/Footballer-Quinn-makes-stand-charity.html|title=Footballer Quinn makes stand for charity|work=Mail Online|accessdate=1 May 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304121048/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-114528/Footballer-Quinn-makes-stand-charity.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而[[英格蘭欖球代表隊|英格蘭欖球代表隊]]成員[[馬田·莊臣|馬田·莊臣]]於2005年6月4日在[[特維克納姆體育場|-{zh-cn:特瓦克內姆体育场; zh-tw:特維克納姆體育場; zh-hk:卓根咸球場}-]]舉行的告別賽中，邀得多名[[欖球|欖球]]球星助陣，為兒童及癌症慈善團體籌得大量款項<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.le.ac.uk/ebulletin-archive/ebulletin/news/2010-2019/2010/01/npfolder.2010-01-22.8305041209/nparticle.2010-01-25.1403472399/index.html|title=University of Leicester - Martin Johnson - Doctor of Laws - Rugby Union player and Team Manager of the England Rugby Union fifteen|publisher=|accessdate=1 May 2015|archive-date=2019-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191019160750/https://www.le.ac.uk/ebulletin-archive/ebulletin/news/2010-2019/2010/01/npfolder.2010-01-22.8305041209/nparticle.2010-01-25.1403472399/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年9月4日，為{{fc|利物浦}}效力15年的[[加歷查|加歷查]]在[[晏菲路球場|晏菲路球場]]舉行的告別賽，為他的「23基金」籌得過百萬英鎊的善款。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.liverpoolfc.tv/news/latest-news/carra-on-target-in-derby-win|title=Carra on target in derby win|work=Liverpool FC|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100907191820/http://www.liverpoolfc.tv/news/latest-news/carra-on-target-in-derby-win|archivedate=2010-09-07|accessdate=2015-05-01}}</ref>

2013年9月，[[侯斯頓戴拿模|侯斯頓戴拿模]]宣布舉行[[美職聯|美職聯]]史上首場告別賽，以表揚即場退休的前鋒[[程拜仁|程拜仁]]。在9月13日舉行的比賽中，戴拿模方面更盡邀球會名宿及其他美職球星助陣。籌得款項已撥入程拜仁創辦的慈善團體「程之家」以及[[國際仁人家園|國際仁人家園]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.houstondynamo.com/chingtestimonial|title=Brian Ching Testimonial Match|work=Houston Dynamo|accessdate=2015-05-01|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112041301/https://www.houstondynamo.com/chingtestimonial|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

